## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not capture all aspects of globalization's impact on people. The data is limited to the perspectives and research available up to October 2023, and newer developments or studies may not be included. Additionally, the complexity of globalization means that its effects can vary significantly across different regions and populations, which may not be fully represented in this report.

